data.description: Live by Lake Cunningham and have easy access to I-680, in this large 3 bedroom/2.5bath split foyer home.  Having 1220 sq ft on the main level, the space is plentiful and offers a large kitchen, dining, and living room area. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and 3/4 bathroom. There's extra living space in the lower level, with a fireplace.  Some cosmetic updates are needed but, the roof and mechanicals are newer. Take a look today and make this house your home!
